                     <interp inst="t18250915-359-off1949" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250915-359-cd1950" type="crimeDate">20th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-359-off1949 t18250915-359-cd1950"></join>, fifteen pairs of boots, value 3 l. 15 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-359-victim1815" type="victimName">
                        George 
                        Miller
                     <interp inst="t18250915-359-victim1815" type="surname" value="Miller"></interp>
